data.description: Lovely all brick 5 bedroom 3 bath home, well suited for entertaining or a large family. The main level boasts 4 bedrooms and 2 baths with hardwoods in the foyer, living room, dining room, eat-in kitchen and den. Den features a beautiful brick fireplace with gas logs, built-in bookcases and leads out to a large patio and fenced back yard. Downstairs offers a bedroom suite, complete with large walk-in closet and full bath, kitchen, and den with private entrance. Basement level 2 car garage and storage room. Washer /dryer hookups on both floors. Walking distance to Gwin Elementary, convenient to shops and restaurants.
